transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan ji India Mart se baat kar rahe hain, bataiye kya help kar sakte hain?
Customer: Phone baat kar rahe hain.
Executive: Kisse baat karna tha? Aap bataiye kisse baat karna tha?
Customer: Haan?
Executive: Aapne lagaya sir phone, bataiye kisse baat karni hai?
Customer: Aapka naam kya hai?
Executive: Aapne sir kahaan phone lagaya sir, kisse baat karni hai bataiye?
Customer: Main India Mart se bol raha hu aap.
Executive: Kahaan se baat kar rahe hain sir aap? Aap India Mart se baat kar rahe hain?
Customer: Arre aap phone lagaye aapka naam toh gin.
